{"tid":1817560,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港人  唔好再逃避","createTime":"2020-01-09T07:51:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-10T11:39:58.000Z","uid":282534,"like":112,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":50,"replies":[{"pid":"42a3f8a1f1a62f38cf89e6a008e6d6e7e0bcf7de","tid":1817560,"uid":282534,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:51:13.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人  <br />\n唔好再逃避</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n最近的確係有好多勇武小隊解散<br />\n<br />\n但作為一個香港人  麻煩你唔好逃避<br />\n唔好將抗爭負責放係勇武身上<br />\n唔好將抗爭責任放係和理身上<br />\n唔好將抗爭責任放係其他人身上<br />\n<br />\n大家成日諗 勇武要點做  和理要點做<br />\n<br />\n不如諗下<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">我</span></strong></span>  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">要點做</span></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">我</span></strong></span>  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以點做</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我</strong></span>  <span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: brown;\">黎緊點做</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我</strong></span>  <span style=\"font-size: large;\">係一個香港人</span> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我</strong></span>  叫 SUCKER<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我</strong></span>  係一條TG Channel owner<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我</strong></span>  同我團體會繼續發起行動<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我</strong></span>  黎緊仲會繼續將勇武既行動做成教材<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>我</strong></span>  <span style=\"color: red;\">同你一樣只係個平凡的人</span><br />\n<br />\n好希望大家可以繼續思考<br />\n自己係呢場抗爭既角色<br />\n同仔細諗下  自己可以做咩<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n有句說話好好<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">改變其他人係好困難<br />\n但你絕對可以<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">改變自己</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\nsorry for 1999  <br />\n<br />\n我地曾經想放棄過 <br />\n但諗到有手足連自己既生命都付出左<br />\n我地決定堅持到最後<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n黎緊農歷新年  我地依然會發起行動  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n為大家附上一條我地channel 出既video<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">[mv]  半年抗爭  we will continue  <br />\n</span><br />\n<a href=\"https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=DUJugrWyYc0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DDUJugrWyYc0&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0y8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=97261deb\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.youtube.com/watch?v=DUJugrWyYc0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n#2為 SUCK 自我介紹  <br />\n#3為 SUCK 部份文宣<br />\n<br />\n或者 有人已經識我地 有人唔識<br />\n但係度再同大家重新介紹一次"},{"pid":"e5b626946f779ea662c2c89875af14651f55181f","tid":1817560,"uid":282534,"like":16,"dislike":2,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-09T07:51:35.000Z","msg":"#2<br />\n我地係SUCK  一條Telegram上既channel<br />\n<br />\n我地係一條會發起行動既channel <br />\n<br />\n或者你唔識我地  <br />\n但絕對有見過我地既文宣<br />\n<br />\n我地發起過既行動<br />\n<br />\n8.24  和你塞<br />\n9.01  和你塞2.0 <br />\n9.07  和你SUCK 3.0<br />\n9.13  中秋獅子山無人機幻演<br />\n9.22  SUCK 4.0 <br />\n10.1  SUCK泥馬<br />\n10.2  三罷不合作行動 <br />\n10.13  [罷鷲] 行動<br />\n10.26  [長龍] 爆買日<br />\n11.12  [破曉] 黎明行動<br />\n11.14  [曙光] 黎明行動<br />\n11.18-22  公務員扮工SUCK <br />\n12.25-26  SUCK the Christmas<br />\n12.31  除夕跨年SUCK <br />\n<br />\n<br />\nWe are SUCK  <br />\nWe never giveup <br />\n<br />\n抗爭黎到呢步  <br />\n我地唔會放棄  <br />\n亦唔可以放棄<br />\n<br />\nSUCK channel : <a href=\"http://t.me/stuckwithyou\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstuckwithyou&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0y8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=4dbe0e0b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">t.me/stuckwithyou</a><br />\n<br />\nfacebook : <a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/tgsuckchannel\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Ftgsuckchannel&d=y5xLblNGdgzQkswvdzbF0y8EbckYnMoWLUJTUpLSOd8%3D&h=8fdce2ca